24
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:53,200
**Gi Da-yong:** Ah, the Baros Island where I was, was an island that you could walk around in 15 minutes. If you go snorkeling for 30 minutes to an hour, you can go all around the island. After living on such an island, when I heard about cruise crew members, I thought, “Now I can go out to the United States.” And cruise crew members are similar to hoteliers. Many people describe the job itself as a floating hotel. It’s also often called an inclusive hotel. At that time, the cruise line that was trying to cross over to Asia was Princess Cruises.

25
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:56,000
