26
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:28,400
**Cho Seon-ju:** Oh, I was so surprised that it sounded like you were telling my story. I was in Bali. Bali is an island. I need to escape from here too. I worked at a resort in Bali for about two years. Cruises occasionally float in the sea in Bali. My Romanian friend said she wanted to get on a ship like that if she escaped from Bali. So that friend posted a picture of her on the ship on Facebook.

27
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,800
**Host:** You went along with your friend.

28
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:42,400
