33
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:30,800
**Lee Se-guk:** It’s been my dream since I was young. I wanted to try cooking on a cruise. But at that time, when I was working as a head chef at a Korean restaurant in the Czech Republic, a chef came for an interview from Korea. This guy submitted resumes for the cruise and the Korean restaurant. But what he said was that he failed the cruise chef position and got accepted here, so he came here.

34
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:33,200
